DISCLAIMER:

- This repo is a proof of concept. Learn Flatpak and clean it up!

Usage:

flatpak-builder build-dir php-game.json --force-clean --user --install && flatpak run my.php.game

To upload online:

flatpak-builder --repo=REPO build-dir php-game.json
(then upload REPO dir to a website)
(then upload flatpakref to a website, make sure it has your correct UR)

To install:

flatpak install --user http://blane.jookia.org/game.flatpakref

Then run flatpak run my.php.game
